<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>Document</title>
    <style>
        .one-bot{
            height:300px;
            width: 600px;
            background-color: #676867;
        }
        #one-cover{
            height: 100px;
            width: 350px;
            background-color: black;
            margin: 0 auto;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }
        .two-bot{
            height:300px;
            width: 600px;
            background-color: rgb(240, 190, 190);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }
        #two-cover{
            height: 100px;
            width: 350px;
            background-color: rgb(169, 207, 133);
            align-self: center;
        }
        .three-bot{
            height:300px;
            width: 600px;
            background-color: #676867;
            display: table-cell;
        }
        #three-cover{
            height: 100px;
            width: 350px;
            background-color: black;
            margin-left: 125px;
            color: white;
        }
        .four-bot{
            height:300px;
            width: 600px;
            background-color: rgb(240, 190, 190);
            position: absolute;
        }
        #four-cover{
            height: 100px;
            width: 350px;
            margin-left: 125px;
            background-color: rgb(169, 207, 133);
        }
        .five-bot{
            margin-top: 300px; 
            height:300px; 
            width: 600px;
            background-color: #676867;
        }
        #five-cover{
            height: 100px;
            width: fit-content;
            background-color: black;
            margin:0 auto;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }
        .six-bot{
            margin-top: 1px;
            height:300px;
            width: 600px;
            background-color: rgb(240, 190, 190);
            display: inline-block;
        }
        #six-cover{
            height: 100px;
            width: 350px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: rgb(169, 207, 133);
        }
        .seven-bot{
            height:300px;
            width: 600px;
            background-color: #676867;
            position: relative;
        }
        #seven-cover{
            height: 100px;
            width: 350px;
            background-color: black;
            float: left;
            margin-left: 125px;
            color: white;
        }
        .eight-bot{
            margin-top: 1px;
            height:300px;
            width: 600px;
            background-color: rgb(240, 190, 190);
            display: inline-block;
        }
        #hide{
            height: 100px;
            width: 125px;
            float: left;
        }
        #eight-cover{
            height: 100px;
            width: 350px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: rgb(169, 207, 133);
        }
        .nine-bot{
            height:300px;
            width: 600px;
            background-color: #676867;
        }
        #nine-cover{
            height: 50%;
            width: 50%;
            text-align: center;
            position: absolute;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-25%,-25%)
            background-color: black;
        }
        .one-per{
            height: 300px;
            width: 100px;
            background-color: rgb(62, 128, 226);
        }
        #one-ver{
            height: 50%;
            width: 50%;
            background-color: rgb(241, 224, 69);
            display: inline-block;
            vertical-align: middle;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .two-per{
            height: 300px;
            width: 100px;
            background-color: rgb(143, 240, 147);
            display: flex;
        }
        #two-ver{
            width: 50%;
            height: 50%;
            background-color: rgb(245, 72, 159);
            align-self: center;
            
        }
        .three-per{
            height: 300px;
            width: 100px;
            background-color: rgb(62, 128, 226);
            display: block;
        }
        .three-per::before{
            content: '';
            display: inline-block;
            vertical-align: middle;
            height: 100%;
        }
        #three-ver{
            height: 50%;
            width: 50%;
            background-color: rgb(241, 224, 69);
            display: inline-block;
            vertical-align: middle;
        }
        .four-per{
            height: 300px;
            width: 100px;
            background-color: rgb(143, 240, 147);
            display: table;
        }
        #four-ver{
            width: 50%;
            height: 50%;
            background-color: rgb(245, 72, 159);
            display: table-cell;
            vertical-align: middle;
        }
        .five-per{
            height: 300px;
            width: 100px;
            background-color: rgb(62, 128, 226);
        }
        #five-hide{
            width: 25%;
            height: 25%;
        }
        #five-ver{
            height: 50%;
            width: 50%;
            background-color: rgb(241, 224, 69);
        }
        .six-per{
            height: 300px;
            width: 100px;
            background-color: rgb(143, 240, 147);
        }
        #six-ver{
            width: 50%;
            height: 50%;
            background-color: rgb(245, 72, 159);
            position: relative;
            top: 50%;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
        }
        .seven-per{
            height: 300px;
            width: 100px;
            background-color: rgb(62, 128, 226);
            position: relative;
        }
        
        #seven-ver{
            height: 50%;
            width: 50%;
            background-color: rgb(241, 224, 69);
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
        }
        .eight-per{
            height: 300px;
            width: 100px;
            background-color: rgb(62, 128, 226);
        }
        #eight-ver{
            width: 50%;
            height: 50%;
            line-height: 300px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <h3>水平居中的九种方法</h3>
    <div class="one-bot">
        <div id="one-cover"> ① </div>
    </div>
    <div class="two-bot">
            <div id="two-cover"> ② </div>
    </div>
    <div class="three-bot">
            <div id="three-cover"> ③ </div>
    </div>
    <div class="four-bot">
            <div id="four-cover"> ④ </div>
    </div>
    <div class="five-bot">
            <div id="five-cover"> ⑤ </div>
    </div>
    <div class="six-bot">
            <div id="six-cover"> ⑥ </div>
    </div>
    <div class="seven-bot">
            <div id="seven-cover"> ⑦ </div>
    </div>
    <div class="eight-bot">
            <div id="hide"></div>
            <div id="eight-cover"> ⑧ </div>
    </div>
    <div class="nine-bot">
            <div id="nine-cover"> ⑨ </div>
    </div>
    <h3>垂直居中的八种方法</h3>
    <div class="one-per">
        <div id="one-ver"> ① </div>
    </div>
    <div class="two-per">
            <div id="two-ver"> ② </div>
    </div>
    <div class="three-per">
        <div id="three-ver"> ③ </div>
    </div>
    <div class="four-per">
        <div id="four-ver"> ④ </div>
    </div>
    <div class="five-per">
        <div id="five-hide"></div>
        <div id="five-ver"> ⑤ </div>
    </div>
    <div class="six-per">
        <div id="six-ver"> ⑥ </div>
    </div>
    <div class="seven-per">
        <div id="seven-ver"> ⑦ </div>
    </div>
    <div class="eight-per">
        <p id="eight-ver"> ⑧ </p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
